abstract: Though its income fell, the company reported higher revenue in the quarter.
snippet: Though its income fell, the company reported higher revenue in the quarter.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO  John T. Chambers, Cisco Systems’ chief executive, did little Wednesday to lift the dark cloud hanging over his company by reporting sluggish growth in its fiscal second quarter and making a disappointing forecast.

headline.main: Cisco Results Top Forecasts, But Growth Is Sluggish
headline.print_headline: Cisco Results Top Forecasts, But Growth Is Sluggish
